text: Bożena Wojtkowska-Haracz (born 28 October 1962) is a Polish badminton player. She competed in women's doubles at the 1992 Summer Olympics in Barcelona. ==References== ==External links== * Category:1962 births Category:Living people Category:Polish female badminton players Category:Olympic badminton players of Poland Category:Badminton players at the 1992 Summer Olympics Category:People from Głubczyce
